high_descs: turn right and walk over to the left side of the bathroom sink
grab a bar of soap out of the trash bin to the lower left of the bathroom sink
turn right to face the bathroom sink properly
place the soap inside the sink, rinse it off, then take it back out
turn right and walk over to the toilet, then hang a left and walk over to the green drawer cabinets on the left side of the room
place the soap inside one of the drawers of the cabinet there
anns.task_desc: place a bar of soap inside the drawers of the bathroom cabinet

high_descs: Move to the side of the sink where the container is below it.
Take the bar of soap out of the container.
Move around and face the sink.
Rinse the bar of soap off in the sink with water , remove after you turn the water off.
Turn around and go to the storage table on the wall behind you.
Put the bar of soap in the third drawer from the right end at the bottom of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bar of soap in the storage table once it is rinsed off.

high_descs: Turn right and move to stand facing the black trash bin.
Pick up the pink bar of soap from inside the trash bin.
Turn right to face the sink.
Place the soap in the sink, turn on the water, and then remove once rinsed.
Turn right and cross the room to the cabinet with the green drawers and stand at the very center, lined up with the lotion.
Open the bottom drawer, second from the left and put the soap inside.
anns.task_desc: Move a rinse bar of soap to a drawer.
